Added a methoxy group to the difluorinated naphthalene structure to increase electron density and provide additional sites for weak interactions with CO2
Added an acetamide group to the difluorinated naphthalene structure to introduce additional hydrogen bonding sites
Added a sulfonamide group to the difluorinated naphthalene structure to introduce additional polar interactions
